# Club Voting System Project Brief

## Project Overview

This project aims to build a comprehensive online voting and club management platform that helps educational institutions and organizations manage their clubs, elections, and voting processes efficiently. The platform provides a secure, transparent, and user-friendly environment for managing club operations, elections, and member participation.

## Strategic Goals

- Create a centralized hub for club management and voting processes
- Provide secure and transparent election mechanisms
- Streamline club operations and member management
- Establish a reliable platform for democratic processes within organizations
- Build an efficient system for handling multiple concurrent elections

## Key Features

### Multi-Role System

- User roles with specific permissions (Users, Candidates, Admins, Club Admins)
- Role-based access control
- Secure authentication and authorization
- Profile management for all user types

### Club Management

- Comprehensive club creation and management
- Position definition and tracking
- Membership management system
- Club status monitoring (Active/Inactive/Pending)
- Detailed club profiles and information

### Nomination System

- Nomination period management
- Candidate application processing
- Application review workflow
- Candidate profile management
- Statement and qualification tracking

### Voting System

- Secure election scheduling and management
- One-vote-per-user enforcement
- Real-time election result tracking
- Support for multiple simultaneous elections
- Vote verification and audit trails

### Support System

- Ticket-based support management
- Priority level assignment (Low/Medium/High/Urgent)
- Status tracking workflow (Open/In Progress/Resolved/Closed)
- Message threading between staff and users

## Technical Requirements

- Mobile-responsive design for accessibility
- Fast loading times and optimized performance
- Secure user authentication and data protection
- Scalable database design for multiple clubs and elections
- Real-time updates for election results

## Design Guidelines

- Clean, intuitive interface prioritizing usability
- Clear navigation and information hierarchy
- Consistent visual language throughout the platform
- Emphasis on accessibility and ease of use
- Visual distinctions between different user roles and sections

## Success Metrics

- User adoption and engagement rates
- Election participation statistics
- Support ticket resolution times
- System uptime and performance
- User satisfaction ratings

## Implementation Phases

### Phase 1: Core Features

- Basic user authentication and role management
- Club creation and management
- Simple election setup and voting mechanism
- Basic support ticket system

### Phase 2: Enhanced Features

- Advanced voting system with real-time results
- Comprehensive nomination process
- Enhanced club management tools
- Improved support system with priority handling

### Phase 3: Advanced Features

- Analytics and reporting dashboard
- Advanced security features
- API for potential integrations
- Enhanced user experience improvements

## Technology Stack

- Backend: Laravel 12.x (PHP 8.2+)
- Frontend: React 19.x with TypeScript
- UI: Tailwind CSS with shadcn/ui components
- Icons: Lucide
- Build Tool: Vite
- Server-Side Framework: Inertia.js
